public class ProtocolException
extends DeveloperException

Generically represents an exception caused by an error in handling of a network protocol. For example, an HTTP response with a 400 code would throw this exception.

Constructor Detail

ProtocolException

public ProtocolException(String message)
Instantiates a ProtocolException with the specified message. It inherits print stack trace flag from the super class; and sets the fatal and inform user flags to false. Makes use of DeveloperException.DeveloperException(String).

Parameters:
message - the error message
